  "instructions": [
    "Prepare Soaked Rice Crumbs by soaking 1 cup of rice in water overnight, then drain and dry thoroughly.",
    "Mix Thai Fish Sauce with Soaked Rice Crumbs until well combined. Add Tamarind Paste, Water, Garlic, Green Chilies, Sesame Seeds, Cumin Seeds, Red Chili Powder, and Ground Black Pepper into the mixture.",
    "Stir continuously over medium heat until it thickens to a crumbly consistency. Adjust seasoning with Sugar if needed.",
